title: Spencerport Rangers announce new boys swim coach
text: Spencerport Rangers announce new boys swim coach Comment Posted Sep. 30, 2015 at 3:16 PM Posted Sep. 30, 2015 at 3:16 PM Greece, N.Y. Sara Smith recently was named head coach for the Spencerport Rangers varsity boys swim team. Smith is a graduate of Nazareth College and a certified U.S. swimming coach.
